{"tid":2022363,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺「五毛」有啲被濫用","createTime":"2020-05-18T09:36:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T09:40:53.000Z","uid":21141,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2d2bb5a78d263a57ffaafeb601ac9f44444e5b13","tid":2022363,"uid":21141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T09:36:13.000Z","msg":"以前多數都係指收錢開post，留言嗰啲先叫五毛。但依家真心膠藍屍，熱狗，假膠，總之持相反意見就被歸類左做五毛。<br />\n<br />\n五毛收錢幫黨做野，但係其他個啲就免費幫黨做野。本質上明明都唔同，但係連登一言不合就屈毛，我覺得對啲真五毛好不敬，呢啲明明係人地既專業來<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2571b34d992c56545f89c1c17639128aa3be208b","tid":2022363,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T09:40:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n要識玩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n周姐輪都無啦啦變黃又得<br />\n立既變黃都得<br />\n</span>"}]}